Package org.neo4j.graphdb.factory.module.edition

Class AbstractEditionModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.graphdb.factory.module.edition.AbstractEditionModule
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    StandaloneEditionModule
    public abstract class AbstractEditionModule
extends Object
    Edition module for DatabaseManagementServiceFactory. Implementations of this class need to create all the services that would be specific for a particular edition of the database.
